communications for customers, employees and investors. Clients have included Aon, HSBC Investment Banking, AkzoNobel, SSAFA, Oxford GlycoScience and Reuters. Now you can draw on\xc2\xa0my\xc2\xa0knowledge and experience to help you achieve your marketing and business objectives.\nOutside work, I use social media and speaking engagements to champion innovation and culture in East Anglia. My aim is to encourage more people to visit our region and more\xc2\xa0businesses to invest here. The Eastern Daily Press called me \xe2\x80\x9cone of the top 20 tweeters in the region.\xe2\x80\x9d While the EDP Norfolk Magazine called me \xe2\x80\x9ca great Norfolk online ambassador.\xe2\x80\x9d\nIn November 2017 I joined the board of the Norfolk Chamber of Commerce as a non-executive director. I look forward supporting our business community and ensuring the Chamber stays relevant to its members. Please let me know if there are any issues you would like to discuss.\nYou are welcome to contact Huw Sayer by phone, email or LinkedIn.T: +44 (0) 20 7193 4806\n\xc2\xa0View Huw Sayers profile\nEmailHuw Sayer presenting #DynamicEast on Mustard TVExploring the dynamic business sectors of Norfolk and Suffolk - October 2016.When Mustard TV invited Huw to share his passion for enterprise in the East of England with a wider audience, he leapt at the chance. Working with the producer and camera crew, Huw helped create\xc2\xa0six programmes exploring the dynamic business communities in Norfolk and Suffolk. As well as drafting the scripts, Huw\xc2\xa0conducted the interviews and (for the first time) presented the series.\xc2\xa0\nNow you can watch all six programmes on YouTube  see the link below.\n\nIf youd like Huw to present your corporate video or do any voice-over work, please get in touch.\n\n \n\nPlease share this page - thank you:EmailLinkedInTwitterSkypeMoreRedditTumblrPinterestFacebookLike this:Like Loading... \n\n\n\n\n\n\nFollow @HuwSayer ON TWITTER  Tweets by @HuwSayer\n\n\nHuws Perso